Iglesia Universal, or in English “The Universal Church”, is growing. Be sure to visit The Iglesia Universal website to find a location near you. The Iglesia Universal is driven by the love its pastors, volunteers and faithful congregants have for God and His mission on Earth. Those who are part of this amazing work make all efforts necessary to take the good news of deliverance, family restoration and salvation to the minds and hearts of those near and far. Today, The Iglesia Universal has hundreds of locations in countries around the world.